    look flummoxed.

    “Doctor, is something wrong?” Her dad asked worriedly. Doctor Aiuchi
    nervously chuckled.

    “Well... it's not dire, but it is a complication.”

    #AO3.scene-break()

    Homura Akemi\'s performance was subpar all morning, and now she felt
