    #AO3.scene-break()

    “Well, she shouldn't have gotten far, and when we do find her... well you
    said she was an orphan right?” Her mom caught as the nurse nodded.
    “Well, we'll take care of her. Our home is her home.”

    “Well legally they do become your wards if their parents are absent or
