    annoyance at Mami for the plan, which lasted until her mom got home
    after dinner, drunk after a long day where the company celebrated her
    daughter's good fortune and her mom's new daughter-in-law. Her mom
    drunkenly didn't notice Homura, but with how chatty she was with Mami,
    Homura didn't mind at all.]

    #emph[When Homura got her... hopefully not vengeance but a different word
    that meant the same thing but less mean... on Mami, she did help her
    disengage Mami and get the three of them to bed with the power of her
    ‘new heart'.]

    #emph[“Wait, was that Homura... or am I seeing things?” Her mom asked as
